BigJob with plugable communication & coordination backends

current supported backends:

A) REDIS, http://redis.io/
B) ZMQ (ZeroMQ), http://www.zeromq.org/

***************************************************************************
A REDIS

1.) Install and run Redis (http://redis.io/)

Mac Homebrew:
brew install redis redis-tools hiredis

Linux:
Download Redis http://redis.io/download
Currently only tested with Redis 2.2.12
1.1) untar 
1.2) make
1.3) make install (if root)


Start Redis (redis-server executable is located in src/ dir):

cd src
./redis-server


2.) Configure Redis Host and Port:
Adjust parameter on top of bigjob_coordination_redis.py

3) Adjust backend config in big_redis.py and big_agent_redis.py

***************************************************************************
B ZMQ

1.) Install ZeroMQ and pyzmq

http://www.zeromq.org/intro:get-the-software
http://zeromq.github.com/pyzmq/index.html


2.) Adjust backend config in big_redis.py and big_agent_redis.py 